      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $n,p \\in \\N^*$ avec $n \\ge p$.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n,p \\in \\N^*\\)</span> avec <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n \\ge p\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "6d5cf2fa-4b5e-4857-ae24-a85853bf2cf9",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "V{\\'e}rifier que $C_n^kC_k^p = C_n^pC_{n-p}^{k-p}$ pour $p \\le k \\le n$.",
        "html": "<p>V<span>é</span>rifier que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(C_n^kC_k^p = C_n^pC_{n-p}^{k-p}\\)</span> pour <span class=\"math inline\">\\(p \\le k \\le n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "8fb78b22-f313-45ae-9ba1-69ea2ea7d3fd",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Calculer $\\sum_{k=0}^n \\,(-1)^kC_n^kC_k^p$.",
        "html": "<p>Calculer <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum_{k=0}^n \\,(-1)^kC_n^kC_k^p\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "3efff28d-a645-4427-88c6-fc4eccd4f1e4",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "En d{\\'e}duire $\\sum_{k=0}^n (-1)^kC_n^kk^p = 0$ si $p < n$.",
        "html": "<p>En d<span>é</span>duire <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\sum_{k=0}^n (-1)^kC_n^kk^p = 0\\)</span> si <span class=\"math inline\">\\(p &lt; n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "535b2d10-cbac-4970-a4d8-c51da4a98a0a",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$0$ si $p < n$, $(-1)^n$ si $p = n$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(0\\)</span> si <span class=\"math inline\">\\(p &lt; n\\)</span>, <span class=\"math inline\">\\((-1)^n\\)</span> si <span class=\"math inline\">\\(p = n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
  ]
